<section id="projetos">
  <div class="section-label">02 — Projetos</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">O que já<br>construí.</h2>
  <div class="projects-grid">

    <a href="#" class="project-card">
      <div class="project-num">001</div>
      <div class="project-arrow">↗</div>
      <div class="project-title">KickOFF-Match</div>
      <p class="project-desc">TCC desenvolvido, com foco em criar um website para criação e organização de partidas esportivas amadoras</p>
      <div class="project-tags">
        <span class="tag">React</span>
        <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="#" class="project-card">
      <div class="project-num">002</div>
      <div class="project-arrow">↗</div>
      <div class="project-title">FFT - Future Focus Test</div>
      <p class="project-desc">Aplicação web, sendo um teste vocacional de cursos superiores, idealizado com python e flask</p>
      <div class="project-tags">
        <span class="tag">Flask</span>
        <span class="tag">Python</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="#" class="project-card">
      <div class="project-num">003</div>
      <div class="project-arrow">↗</div>
      <div class="project-title">Nome do Projeto</div>
      <p class="project-desc">Descrição curta do projeto. O que ele faz e qual problema resolve.</p>
      <div class="project-tags">
        <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="tag">CSS</span>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #projetos {
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 1px solid #D8D4CC;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: #C84B31;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    border: 1.5px solid #D8D4CC;
  }
  .project-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #F7F5F0;
    border-right: 1.5px solid #D8D4CC;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #D8D4CC;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
  }
  .project-card:hover { background: #EDEAE3; }
  .project-card:hover .project-arrow {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(0, 0);
  }
  .project-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #C84B31;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .project-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(-4px, 4px);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    color: #C84B31;
  }
  .project-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: #141210;
  }
  .project-desc {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #6B6760;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
  .project-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    background: #F0E6E2;
    color: #C84B31;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>